<h2>Q2 2009</h2>

<p>We've kicked off 2009 with a bang on a few fronts. First, in mid-January, we released the first public milestone of Nova to everyone to use. Then, 6 weeks later, we release the second build to the community a full 4 weeks ahead of schedule. In the coming quarter, our focus is solely on getting milestone 4 completed. Doing so would be us beyond the halfway point in development. There will be lots of information available on the blog as well as the forums in the coming weeks and months, so make sure to stay tuned for lots of Nova stuff!</p>

